item.title: Projects
item.description: Projects Here are my coding projects from that I completed for Computational Bio class at UT during my Spring 2020 semester: Exploratory Data Analysis with Tidyverse Tools: Beyoncé versus Solange Modeling, Testing, and Classification of Beyoncé and Solange’s Music BIG thank you to my professor, Nathaniel Woodward (PLEASE TAKE HIM IF YOU HAVE THE CHANCE) for helping me learn how to use Spotify’s API! I know so much more about the music I stream and how Spotify works because of him.
